OL,3,CFather and sons jailed after beating
OL,4,Cman to death for his two Rolex watches
OL,6,FA father and his two sons have been
OL,7,Fjailed for beating a man to death with
OL,8,Fa wrench in in broad daylight, for his
OL,9,Ftwo Rolex watches.
OL,11,FLee O'Brien, 51, and sons Luke, 36,
OL,12,Fand Lewis, 31, ambushed Darren Smith
OL,13,Foutside a row of shops in broad
OL,14,Fdaylight in , on March 15 last year.
OL,15,FThe 51-year-old had been to a phone
OL,16,Fshop to buy a new mobile phone case
OL,17,Fwhen he was beaten by the trio on
OL,18,FHeath Way.
OL,20,FHe was repeatedly punched and kicked,
OL,21,Fand hit with a wrench.
