OL,3,CFather and sons jailed after beating
OL,4,Cman to death for his two Rolex watches
OL,6,FThey stole two Rolex watches from
OL,7,FDarren's wrist and threatened shop
OL,8,Fstaff before fleeing in their cars.
OL,10,FDarren walked unsteadily out of the
OL,11,Fshop, before collapsing nearby, where
OL,12,Fmembers of the public gave first aid
OL,13,Funtil emergency services arrived.
OL,15,FHe was pronounced dead at the scene,
OL,16,Fafter suffering severe head injuries
OL,17,Fand a heart attack.
OL,19,FLee O'Brien and his two sons Luke and
OL,20,FLewis fled to Torquay in a friend's
OL,21,Fcar - which was then traced by police.
