OL,3,CFather and sons jailed after beating
OL,4,Cman to death for his two Rolex watches
OL,6,FThey were arrested the following day,
OL,7,Fon 16 March 2023.
OL,9,FAt Birmingham Crown Court last
OL,10,FSeptember Lee O'Brien, 51, Luke
OL,11,FO'Brien, 36 and Lewis O'Brien 31, all
OL,12,Fpleaded guilty to manslaughter.
OL,14,FOn Friday 5 April 2024, Lewis O'Brien
OL,15,Fand Luke O'Brien were both jailed for
OL,16,F12-and-a-half-years and Lee O'Brien
OL,17,Fwas jailed for 11 years and eight
OL,18,Fmonths.
