OL,6,FDetective Inspector Michelle Thurgood
OL,7,Ffrom our Homicide Team, said: "We know
OL,8,Fthat Lee, Luke and Lewis all knew
OL,9,FDarren. They robbed him but claimed
OL,10,Fthat they did not intend to kill him.
OL,12,F"My thought's remain with Mr Smith's
OL,13,Ffamily at this distressing time, I
OL,14,Fhope that these sentences bring them
OL,15,Fsome sense of justice being done."
OL,17,FDarren's family previously released
OL,18,Fthis tribute: "We as a family are
OL,19,Fdevastated at the loss of our son
OL,20,FDarren.
